{"tid":1849274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"第七個月啦！仲要人幫你罷工？你知唔知醜？","createTime":"2020-01-29T03:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T04:01:32.000Z","uid":212349,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ead6b69af734b2d0ae87bfa967a9343d11cb3871","tid":1849274,"uid":212349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:21:45.000Z","msg":"只要肯罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本唔需要黎明行動。罷工嘅人數=集會嘅人數。其實只要好似10.1咁搞五區集會分散警力，勇武手足就可以容易做嘢。<br />\n<br />\n但都係個句，要多人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />10.1其實係一個大成功嘅例子。嗰日所有商舖落閘，全部黨鐵近乎收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f45fa4c7837ba4606ca438a3cdebbdeef4a2848","tid":1849274,"uid":212349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:22:21.000Z","msg":"罷工要自發"},{"pid":"cd49420b060b1e415665577943d40a6d0d19aeca","tid":1849274,"uid":212349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:23:11.000Z","msg":"罷工然後喺屋企瞓覺係冇用，要出嚟集會做勇武既護盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855c7413f46f54630d3a490c3aec0f49b1d4d096","tid":1849274,"uid":145292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43029ccfa0ad278b67ad7fbafd9d62bdd5786e2","tid":1849274,"uid":212349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:26:22.000Z","msg":"大家發唔發現，冇集會嘅罷工，基本上都係失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.5都係一個成功嘅例子。嗰日係有多區集會，罷完工都要知道自己嘅角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9783090e0e88da26d5507bd73fe9a2f5d8c0420b","tid":1849274,"uid":212349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:28:01.000Z","msg":"建議：黎明行動可以照做，但前提係一定要多區集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c063875a0224c5b8fb5f72d743247c0ac80b1743","tid":1849274,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:33:58.000Z","msg":"be water 無大台，要黎明行動嘅手足衡量風險同成効，要集會嘅手足搞集會搞文宣，各自努力無衝突的"},{"pid":"89ac157c4267a2a0941e4dca6bb1a94d5f02e6ec","tid":1849274,"uid":212349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c063875a0224c5b8fb5f72d743247c0ac80b1743","tid":1849274,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:33:58.000Z","msg":"be water 無大台，要黎明行動嘅手足衡量風險同成効，要集會嘅手足搞集會搞文宣，各自努力無衝突的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:38:15.000Z","msg":"最重要真係要肯罷工，如果唔係再多的文宣和黎明行動都是冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0abf45f839e1dacb85aa47dbe729d7aa22227111","tid":1849274,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T04:01:32.000Z","msg":"出去比人話冇腦送頭？<br />\n等香港病死人政府就會做野<br />\n病死多幾個香港人就主動罷工<br />\n反正唔係你死<br />\n個個比藉口自己罷左又點？<br />\n抗疫保衛家園？我呸<br />\n去排口罩就得 唔洗逼政府封關"}]}